Homepage: https://github.com/archerprojects/boot-os-pro
Description: Boot OS Pro — Multiboot USB Creator with Persistent Storage
 Boot OS Pro is a desktop application for creating multiboot USB drives
 that boot via GRUB2 on both legacy BIOS and EFI machines. Each persistent
 OS is extracted into its own dedicated ext4 partition for universal,
 distro-independent persistence, while a shared free space partition holds
 live-session ISOs that boot via loopback.
 .
 Features:
  - GRUB2 installation for EFI (x86_64) and legacy BIOS (i386-pc)
  - Per-ISO dedicated ext4 partition with the OS extracted at write time
  - Universal persistence — no casper-rw overlay, no distro-specific hooks
  - Multiple live-session ISOs in a shared free space partition
  - Self-describing drive via an on-EFI manifest
  - Disk Manager: per-partition format, delete, safe whole-device wipe
  - Live write progress with cancellation support
